        #third_slide_background
          .container#first_slide_3.hide_first_slide

            #second_slide_set_1
              .description_number_parent
                .description_number_container.float-left
                  .float-left.phone_number_container
                    %span.number 1
                  .float-right.phone_content_container
                    Customize Clari for your business, sales process, and CRM requirements

                .description_number_container.float-left
                  .float-left.phone_number_container
                    %span.number 2
                  .float-right.phone_content_container
                    Build Custom Clari Accelerators to maximize data capture

                .description_number_container.float-left
                  .float-left.phone_number_container
                    %span.number 3
                  .float-right.phone_content_container
                    Instantly publish changes to all Clari users in your organizations
                .clear
              %br
              %br
              .ipad_item_container
                = image_tag 'bg-device-ops-1-1.png'
              .clear